speech: At JECRC, for students inclined towards social services we have clubs like Zarurat, SOCH, Aashayein and First Step that are doing commendable job in enriching lives of the underprivileged sections of the society
We have two dance clubs Enigma & Khaalas.
At JECRC dramatics club Face & Footlite, literary club Parijaat, the official college magazine J-Mag, photography club Fotografreaks.
